high_descs: Turn right and go straight into the kitchen area, approaching the area of the counters with the microwave.
Pick up the mug from the counters.
Go to the fridge on the left.
Place the mug in the fridge, let it cool, then remove the mug.
Place the mug into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled Mug into a Microwave.

high_descs: Turn around wall to the kitchen countertop.
Turn around right and pick up the mug in the cup.
Turn around right and left go to the fridge.
Move to the fridge, put in the mug.
Open the microwave in the fridge, turn right and left.
Open the microwave and put the mug in it.
anns.task_desc: Turn around right and pick up the mug. Open the microwave and put the mug in it.

high_descs: Go to kitchen counter by microwave.
Pick up the mug that is on the kitchen counter.
Take the mug to the fridge.
Take mug out of the fridge to the microwave.
Place the mug in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Get mug off counter top, chill in fridge, place in microwave.
